snot - simple notification
==========================
WIP!

Text based notification server for libnotify. 


Planned capabilities:
---------------------
"action-icons"      no
"actions"           yes
"body"              yes
"body-hyperlinks"   no
"body-images"       no
"body-markup"       maybe
"icon-multi"        no
"icon-static"       no
"persistence"       maybe
"sound"             maybe


